texts.text: We can't let him harm Haru and Shiva...
But if we don't stop Shiva, we're dead.
Haru! Can't you stop this?!
>Haru is still dancing under Shiva's control...
I can't! It's like my body's not my own...!
Shiva, please stop! I don't want to do this...!
No! The destruction of evil takes top priority.
But...
No.

But I...
I don't want to kill Fuyuki!
Even if it means sacrificing others, I want Fuyuki to live!
I want to save Fuyuki!
I want to save him so we can be together again!
If he dies, that'll be impossible!
>Haru shouts, but his feet still dance.
>Unmoved by Haru's words, Shiva just stares at Angra Mainyu.
What a cold hearted god you are, Shiva.
You need to be more relaxed, like me... Agh!
What...? How can a mortal...!
>Suddenly, Angra Mainyu doubles over in agony,
>and his summoning begins to ebb.
What's going on?  He's slowing down...
Hey! You hear that?!
Fuyu...ki? Is that you, Fuyuki?!
Haru... I...
I don't... Want this...
Hurting people... Haru will... Be disappointed in me...
I want to be... with you too...
I want to live... By Haru's side...!
Fuyuki!
What Angra Mainyu said... is true...

I think I was... Jealous of you...
But even so...
Haru, I want to live by your side! I want things to go back to the way they were...!
I love you Haru! I have for a long time!
Yes! Me too! I love you too Fuyuki!
Insignificant mortal, how dare you...
Have you forgotten it was I who fulfilled your wish...?
A-Agh!
Hey, what's that!
>Suddenly, a small light appears on Angra Mainyu's chest.
What is this light...? It is inside me...!

!
That light! Can it be?!
Whoa...
Hey, I can move my body!
Fuyuki, can you still hear me?!
Yes, I hear you...! Haru's voice!
Ugh, back off human...! You are weak!
>Each time Haru and Fuyuki call to each other, the light grows stronger.
Yes, that is the great light of Shakti! There is no doubt!
I can feel it! The aura of my consort Parvati!

What...!
Aaaagh!
>Just as Shiva Shouts Parvati's name,
>Angra Mainyu's body shines brighter...!
Now Haru! Take the one called Fuyuki by the hand!
Take his hand?!
It is the only way to save the people here!
I'm not sure I understand... But this will save everybody right?!
Yes!
Well then...!
If this can save Fuyuki...!
Ririn, cover Haru!
Got it Mister Meat!
You shall not...!
You shall not! Pin him down!
>Angra Mainyu attacks Haru with Fuyuki's body,
>But Gakuto's demon blocks the way!
Now Haru!
Fuyukiiii!
Haru...!
>Haru's hand touches Fuyuki's,
>and a bright light fills the entire space.
>A childhood memory springs into Haru and Fuyuki's mind...
C'mon Fuyuki! Quick!
W-Wait for me Haru!
C'mon, over here!
>Haru waves his hands wildly, unaware of the snake descending from a tree branch...!
Haru! Watch out!
Huh...?
Ya!
>Just when the snake is about to strike Haru, Fuyuki shields him from it.
Fuyuki?!
Ouch... Are you okay Haru?
I'm okay, but you're...
I helped my favorite person in the world, so I'm okay.
You're the most important person to me too, so I don't want to see you get hurt...
*Chuckle* You're so nice Haru.
So are you Fuyuki!
Whoa, what's going on?!
It's so bright, I can't see. But this light... It's kinda warm...
>After a while, the light subsides.
This form... What is happening...?
What happened to us...?
The two of us have truly become one, as have you two.
My name is Ardha, Ardhanarishvara in full.
I represent perfect unity. I am the perfect being.
Ardha...? This body?
This is what we are now...?

Those voices...
Are you two in there?!
Yes! I don't know why,
but I can feel Haru's presence close to me!
Tsk, I did not anticipate being driven out like this...
Huh?! Why's Angra Mainyu here?!
When we became one, he was driven out of our union as a foreign object.
I am Ardha, the Perfect One.
You are imperfect, so you cannot win.
Return to the depths of darkness from whence you came, Absolute Evil.

*Cackle*
What an unexpected ending.
But not even you can erase me from existence, no matter how deep you bury me in the abyss.
Begone!
Aaaaaaaargh!
One day, my time will come again!
See you then, Shiva... Or should I say...Ardha!
It is done...
Whoa...
h-Huh?
>Ardha blinks, then Haru and Fuyuki appear hand in hand.
You have my thanks Haru. You as well, Fuyuki.
My union would not have been possible without you.
But I... I...
Haru was all I really needed,
but I became jealous. I wouldn't even admit it to myself...
I am weak... Do I really...
Do I really deserve to be with you Haru? Am I allowed to love you?
I don't care about those things.
As long as you're with me, I'm happy.
Haru...
The feelings you have for each other, that is the great light of Shakti.
Huh...?
Your feelings and your harmony is what summoned me. Have pride in it.
But...
It is a sad thing that the world of Man has yet to achieve perfect harmony,
so people may shun your relationship.
Nevertheless...
My perfect union must be achieved in order to manifest.
You're love for each other is true, my manifestation is a testament to that.
Travel your own path, and find your own answers.
Farewell, ye of gentle Harmony.
>Ardha shines again, and is gone in an instant.
I don't think I understand...
Me neither. But... I'm glad.
Huh?
Because now I know how you feel!
Fuyuki...
Hey guys, I'd hate to break this up but...
Time to haul ass! This place is gonna fall apart!
Yessir!
>A short while after the incident with the evil god and the perfect deity who sealed it...
Hello everybody.
H-Hi guys.
Haru and Fuyuki! What brings you here?
Even though it was only for a short while, they were under the influence of Shiva, Angra Mainyu and Ardha.
You never know what that can do to a person,
so they'll be under the custody of the Liberators. Not here of course.
Oh, I see.
And umm, we're officially a couple now.
No surprise there.
Do you think it's... Odd?
Oh sorry, that's not what I meant! I don't think it's odd at all!
I mean, I'm into girls, so... Cute ones, to be exact.
Maybe that's a bit different from what you guys have...
But I know what I like and so do you,
so I think it's great.
When I was a student, similar couples would hide their relationship from others
because they knew how they'd be treated if people found out.
Now a lot of countries and laws seem to be more inline with the times.
Not that that should matter. I just think you should do what you feel is right.
There are places in the world though where people still look upon these things negatively for religious reasons and stuff.
That god Ardha said it too. The world's not a harmonious place.
This could be what Ardha was talking about.
But even in a world like this, everything'll be alright if you can find your own path.
Someone once said.
Always be yourself. Always express yourself.
Have conviction in yourself.
Remember what Ardha said. Find your own way, travel your own path.
Yes... That makes sense!
But...
...After we announced it, some people blatantly started avoiding Haru.
But I guess that's not a bad thing cuz it gives us more time to be together.
That's a great way to think! Very positive.
If you guys ever feel lonely, I can always keep you company...
>Jeng Yun is just about to put his arm around Haru's shoulder,
>when...
>Fuyuki swiftly takes him by the arm and gives him a nasty stare...!
Just kidding.
Dang! Don't ever do that again! I thought I was gonna have a heart attack!
Hahahaha! Nice moves Fuyuki!
Aw, thanks!
